description: The end of the New Thalos Pier, and also the end of the Great
Realms continent.  This is roughly the most eastern point of the
continent, not including islands like the Dark Continent, Paradise
Island or the 'Chain Islands' between the Sea of Swords and Istar Sea
to the north.  Beyond this pier across the vast Sea of Swords is the
continent of Faerun, home to worldy known cities such as Icewind Dale,
Waterdeep, Daggerford, Baldur's Gate, Candlekeep, Myth Drannor and
Shadowdale.  Sailing and travelling in an eastern direction will bring
you past the Dark Continent and Paradise Island to the docks at 'The
Way Inn', a medium size village and stopping point for people
travelling north and south between Waterdeep and Candlekeep.
